Please be advised that our copyright  
protected intellectual property is currently streaming on a website
managed  
by your company.

In addition to domestic legal and international legal action, we fully  
intend to pursue criminal charges to the fullest extent of the law.

The title in question is the feature film "The Witches of Oz".  If all  
references and links to this film are not removed from this website in the
 
next 24 hours, we will begin legal proceedings.

Regards,
Leigh Scott
